description: ‘dem daugs & burgers is doling out some fantastically flavorful fire-grilled grub.South Carolinians know they can always count on this state-of-the-art mobile kitchen for the best burger fix. The beef is perfectly grilled and packed with smoky flavor, and if you opt to top your meal with the famous fire-grilled chili, you’re just plain in for a treat.The fire-braised chicken sandwiches are tender and savory, the daugs are piled with all the finest toppings, and the funnel cakes and fried oreos? Well you’ll just find ‘dem to be so dang tasty too. For deliciousness you can’t miss, get yourself ‘dem daugs & burgers soon!
name: 'dem daugs & burgers
